{"tid":2518141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"延續川普貿易戰！美商務部長：動用所有選項牽制中國","createTime":"2021-05-05T22:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T00:57:40.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9626a166adab74d050d2c45f02e0196dc6b19992","tid":2518141,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T22:16:17.000Z","msg":"延續川普貿易戰！美商務部長：動用所有選項牽制中國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3493963\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3493963&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQnqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=d77028aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3493963&h=77113d5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3493963</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國商務部長雷蒙多（Gina Raimondo）週三（7日）承諾，川普政府與中國強勢的貿易戰將延續下去，旨在保護美國工作者及企業免於中國不公做法的侵害。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">雷蒙多在白宮記者會上表示，川普任職期間施加的中國關稅，當時雖飽受民主黨批評，但關稅確實拯救了美國鋼鋁產業的就業。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n據報導，美國仍維持對中國66%產品的關稅，雷蒙多表示，為使國際貿易能有1個公平競爭的環境，這些關稅是必要的。<br />\n<br />\n雷蒙多表示：「中國的行為是非競爭性的、脅迫性、卑劣的，他們已被證明會不擇手段達成目標，因此，我計畫動用所有可能選項，盡可能積極保護美國工作者及企業免於中國不公做法的侵害。」<br />\n<br />\n據報導，3年前，川普對許多國家的進口鋼徵收25%關稅，對進口鋁徵收10%關稅。川普稱，這事關國家安全，旨在確保國內鋼鋁產業能夠生存下去。<br />\n<br />\n根據皮尤研究中心去年1項調查，美國近9成的成年人將中國視為競爭者或敵人，而非夥伴。"},{"pid":"3d216953e8f999d0c64e3ad23272e5fd8f1e0a09","tid":2518141,"uid":288675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:23:38.000Z","msg":"Just. Take no action"},{"pid":"041ea4a0a055297e13596089470d7c8b3960f328","tid":2518141,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d216953e8f999d0c64e3ad23272e5fd8f1e0a09","tid":2518141,"uid":288675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:23:38.000Z","msg":"Just. Take no action"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:52:22.000Z","msg":"and keep look around"},{"pid":"ea62028549025019699ae937de28bd82cdcb2aa2","tid":2518141,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:53:54.000Z","msg":"All talk no action"},{"pid":"c027d39d7f0484ddfc6f01a185b33e811da252af","tid":2518141,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:57:40.000Z","msg":"左膠見到肯定唔高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUtspTtnTSx6hqAeyLAdRykcEQNg8d18uYuMudpH2WLjC?filename=R1sRU2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR1sRU2a.png&h=0414b5c0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}